text: "In Too Deep" is a 2001 pop punk song by the rock band Sum 41. It is the second single from their debut studio album All Killer, No Filler, which was released in 2001. The music video for "In Too Deep" is a parody of the diving scene from the movie Back to School. Category:Sum 41 songs Category:2001 songs
title: In Too Deep (Sum 41 song)
